raw_text = "~ needs_sudo_token
Door Console: ACCESS DENIED.
Door Console: Elevated privileges required.
Door Console: This room is protected by sudo policy.
Door Console: A sudo token from Driver Remnant is required.
Door Console: [Educational context: sudo lets non-root users run commands as root]
Door Console: [The token represents verified understanding of privilege escalation]
=> END

~ already_open
Door Console: ACCESS GRANTED.
Door Console: Boss room lock is already disengaged.
Door Console: The privilege gate remains open.
=> END

~ unlocked
Door Console: AUTHENTICATION ACCEPTED.
Door Console: Sudo token verified and consumed.
Door Console: Boss room lock disengaged.
Door Console: Privilege escalation successful. Proceed with caution.
=> END
"
